name: GMA_060_001_PixelArt (1st Collab)
description:
Pixelated version from the Collection GeometricMinimalArt

This is my first collaboration here in HEN with the amazing Artist & Collector @tomivisual.
This Art piece was born out of mutual admiration for each other’s very different styles, and genuine curiosity about how these styles might work together.
So the Generative art piece "the sun is rising now" (OBJKT#253128) created by @tomivisual was transformed in a 3D Rendered Geometric Minimalistic Art piece and then in an elaborated new Pixeleted version for my Hen Collection!

Enjoy!
